{"tid":378213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]兩廢老被捕","createTime":"2017-08-28T10:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T10:55:12.000Z","uid":41166,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4c28da0e8dad5873a32318888fe96662ea28369","tid":378213,"uid":41166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:14:00.000Z","msg":"澳門司警扣留2名73歲和68歲的兄妹，他們涉嫌在網上發佈不實消息，包括聲稱政府封鎖在筷子基停車場發現5具遺體的消息。司警表示，有人未證實消息真確，就用手機通訊軟件「微信」（WeChat），轉載該不實消息到至少6個聊天群組、30個私人對話中。司警會以觸犯侵犯行使公共當局權力之法人罪，移送他們到檢察院。司警又表示，案件仍在調查，不排除有更多人涉案。"},{"pid":"cb1a7b129edf133120f725f4da1273f20f98c98c","tid":378213,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:17:14.000Z","msg":"23條好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b0f5fe4aff5e270e1dae5fe881f430a3be5759","tid":378213,"uid":76216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:18:24.000Z","msg":"用we chat 後果  比人監控 講乜都比人知"},{"pid":"427f1063afd478fcbe700512b1c527316cdb7c0a","tid":378213,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:19:24.000Z","msg":"嘩屌 澳門真係抵死"},{"pid":"a520119ec7041c9e9381687c9c046d011567cab0","tid":378213,"uid":72228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:20:04.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38350081e8853bd2753963b95b225699ea90063b","tid":378213,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8474233a12fb97f9072f7b83874934b01009b12","tid":378213,"uid":810,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/182322_d1e91b8becec7784ac4b006b14fdce35.jpg\" data-th